LTC Hughes - hope you are well!

We will need HF frequencies for TNMAN for the following dates: 13 May (Wedn=
esday) through 15 May (Friday). 3rd Regiment will stand up the HF antenna o=
n Wednesday evening, and we will be sending all day 14 May. There is a chan=
ce we will need it 15 May (Friday), but we anticipate ENDEX on Thursday.

3rd Regiment S3 (LTC Sheaf) and XO (LTC Smith) are both copied this email. =
Please Reply All with any RFIs, or frequency info. Many thanks.

V/R

LTC Estes


